metadata.dc:description: The aims of this study was to analyce cervical not preparation with Gates Glidden bur, Orifice Shaper and ProTaper NiTi rotary instruments. Thirty maxillary molars were prepared with this instruments and analised with the Bramante Berter, Borges technique. Don’t have difference between Gates Glidden but, Orifice Shaper and ProTaper instruments in preparation of the cervical third of root canal But, ProTaper was better maintenance root canal anatomy (AU)
